data.description: Presenting a meticulously maintained ranch-style single family home located in the desirable Sundown North neighborhood positioned for unparalleled convenience. This property boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a 2-car attached garage, encompassing 1,648 square feet of well-designed living space. Upon entry, you will be welcomed by newly laid hardwood floors and all new windows installed on the main level that beams with natural light. In your primary bedroom, you will get to enjoy the newly installed closet that is still under warranty. As you make your way into the kitchen, you will be greeted by all new appliances that are also still under warranty for all of your cooking needs! Entering the finished basement, you have an additional bedroom and bathroom and extra living space to entertain. You will notice the maintenance of the home flows seamlessly into the front and backyard. As the leaves are starting to fall, your leaf gutters will save you! You'll enjoy the charm of this peaceful community while still being minutes away from shops, restaurants, and Powers! Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming home your own!
